					<h2 class="mt-3 mt-md-0"><i class="fas fa-microphone"></i></h2>
					<h3 class="h5 mb-3">Voice assistant</h3>
					<p>Shravan comes with an AI-based assistant that can help you answer emails, make calls, send messages, and do everyday tasks with ease, with natural speech recognition and synthesis.</p>
					<p>The Shravan voice assistant if the first one that works in 11 native Indian languages &mdash; Bengali, English, Gujarati, Kannada, Malayalam, Marathi, Tamil, Telugu, Urdu, Hindi.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="col-md-6">
					<h2 class="mt-3 mt-md-0"><i class="fas fa-newspaper"></i></h2>
					<h3 class="h5 mb-3">News, search, internet</h3>
					<p>Shravan can potentially be the first-of-its-kind internet device for millions of people, so it comes with native language support for news, web search, email, and an HTML5-based low data usage web browser.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
