	<section>
		<div class="container">
			<div class="row">
				<div class="col-md-6">
					<h2 class="mt-3 mt-md-0"><i class="fas fa-music"></i></h2>
					<h3 class="h5 mb-3">Music streaming</h3>
					<p>Users can listen to unlimited free music on their smartphones using Shravan's build-in Music app. Users can use the custom-build YouTube&trade; app with their screens off for free music streaming, or choose to configure their music subscription with Shravan.</p>
					<p>Currently supported streaming services are Apple Music, Gaana, Jio Music, Spotify, Saavn, and Wynk Music.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="col-md-6">
					<h2 class="mt-3 mt-md-0"><i class="fas fa-ambulance"></i></h2>
					<h3 class="h5 mb-3">Health &amp; emergency</h3>
					<p>Shravan users can set up emergency contacts, who can get access to their high-accuracy live location, found using a combination of GPS, mobile towers, and WiFi hotspots. They can also use one-tap ambulance, a service that automatically alerts the authorities in case of an emergency.</p>
					<p>Shravan also comes with a custom-built version of Naari, a period tracking and menstrual health education app for women; and a medication reminder and scheduler for senior citizens.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
	<section class="gray">
