				<div class="col-md-6">
					<h2 class="mt-3 mt-md-0"><i class="fas fa-lock"></i></h2>
					<h3 class="h5 mb-3">Aadhaar integration</h3>
					<p>When you turn on Shravan for the first time, you can choose to enter your Aadhaar number, and the phone will instantly recognize you thereafter. No need to spend countless hours storing your information or verifying one-time passwords.</p>
					<p>Using IndiaStack's Aadhaar API, your information is only accessed after direct consent and authentication, and implements a bank-level 128-bit SSL/TLS security system.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="col-md-6">
					<h2 class="mt-3 mt-md-0"><i class="fas fa-comments"></i></h2>
					<h3 class="h5 mb-3">Free messaging</h3>
					<p>Shravan comes build-in with an unlimited free messaging app for Shravan-to-Shravan users, and support for popular messaging apps such as BBM, Facebook Messenger, LINE, Skype, Telegram, Viber, WeChat, and WhatsApp.</p>
					<p>Shravan Messenger also comes with a Ping feature, using which users can alert and ask for the live locations of their contacts securely.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
