					<h3 class="h5 mb-3">Cashless payments</h3>
					<p>Shravan is the first operating system with build-in support for Unified Payments Interface (UPI). Aadhaar-verified users can make even transactions without manually entering OTPs using Shravan's AutoOTP&trade;. It works across all partner banks, and money is automatically debited to and credited from your bank account.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="col-md-6">
					<h2 class="mt-3 mt-md-0"><i class="fas fa-sync-alt"></i></h2>
					<h3 class="h5 mb-3">Automatic updates</h3>
					<p>Shravan automatically downloads and installs updates when a WiFi connection is detected. Latest security updates, interface changes, and features are automatically added, and user data backed up to the cloud. Users can just enter their Aadhaar number to a new Shravan phone to automatically transfer all their data.</p>
